org.zyp.cn8583
接口 cnSystemTraceNumGenerator

所有已知实现类：
cnSimpleSystemTraceNumGen
public interface cnSystemTraceNumGenerator

这是一个中国版的8583格式标准的接口，初始代码来源于TraceNumberGenerator接口。 This interface defines the behavior needed to provide sequence numbers for newly created messages. It must provide sequence numbers between 1 and 999999, as per the ISO standard. This value is put in field 11. A default version that simply iterates through an int in memory is provided.

作者：
zyplanke
